# Gittan triage changes

If you are editing **`cli_triage`** (implementation or tests), before treating the work as done:

1. In **Cursor**, start a chat and run **`/gittan-triage-review`**, with the diff or `@` files attached.
2. Or open and follow **`.cursor/commands/gittan-triage-review.md`** (same checklist as the slash command).

Canonical contract: **`docs/runbooks/gittan-triage-agents.md`**. Keep **`gittan triage --json`** read-only; watch import edges vs **`core/report_service`**.
